Subject: Complaint regarding inadequate water supply in [Your Area]

Dear Sir/Madam,

I am writing this letter to bring to your attention the ongoing issue of inadequate water supply in [Your Area]. I am a resident of [Your Area] and have been facing this problem for the past few months. Despite several complaints to the local authorities, the situation has not improved.

The water supply in our area is extremely irregular and insufficient. We only receive water for a few hours in a day, and that too at very low pressure. This has caused a lot of inconvenience to the residents, especially during the summer season when the demand for water is high. We are forced to store water in tanks and containers, which is not only time-consuming but also unhygienic.

Moreover, the quality of water supplied is also a matter of concern. The water is often dirty and has a foul smell, making it unfit for consumption. This has led to an increase in water-borne diseases in our area, and the residents, especially children and elderly, are at risk.

